{
  "stem": "9995.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I was giving part of it to the people who gave me cigarettes and part for keeping for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we had really very good food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had cheeses, we have some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kielbasas and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had-- and we had fruit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because, otherwise, people were getting some food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, the English didn't have much, but at that time also, something happened, which I wasn't speaking much before, but now I can.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The English-- and that was my problem with the English, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "General Montgomery, unlike the generals in America, had forbidden the English soldiers to associate with German girls.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since they didn't have the wives or girlfriends or anybody, with whom they going to go out?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With the girls from concentration camp who are recovering nicely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, so, I didn't know about it until one day, I went in the middle of this little town over there, and I see some jeeps and English soldiers who knew German, were saying, come on, girls.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're going to go to a party, you're going to dance, and you're going to have good sandwiches, ice cream.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I run back to our place, and I said-- the other girl, they were two sisters, and one of them was still very sick.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, Lucy, let's go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to have sandwiches, ice cream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember how ice cream and chocolate, everything tastes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, let's-- so she said, terrific.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We go over there, and we go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were several jeeps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We go to that place where the soldier was staying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, there is a party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There is music, dances which we didn't know, Hokey Pokey, and Lambeth Walk and Boops a Daisy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We got to dance first.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
